<?xml version="1.0"?>
<?xml-stylesheet type="text/xsl" href="../isisxsl.xsl"?>
<isis lang="en">
    <stitle>TSI 05-12-28 - New High-Pressure Oil Rails</stitle>
    <tsi id="tsi051228" year="2005" tsitype="engine">
        <tsinumber>05-12-28</tsinumber>
        <tsidate>July 2005</tsidate>
        <subjectfile>Engine</subjectfile>
        <subjectgroup>
            <subject>New High-Pressure Oil Rails</subject>
        </subjectgroup>
        <apply>
            <configure>
                <engfamgroup/>

                <engfam>DT 466
                    <snrange>2,000,001 and up</snrange>
                </engfam>
                <engfam>DT 570
                    <snrange>2,000,001 and up</snrange>
                </engfam>
                <engfam>HT 570
                    <snrange>2,000,001 and up</snrange>
                </engfam>
            </configure>
        </apply>
        <description>
            <geninfo>
                <para>New high-pressure oil rails are a direct replacement for the old and have casting and machining
                    changes which remove internal clearance depths for attenuator assemblies. New high-pressure oil
                    rails can only use oil rail plug assemblies (1, Figure 1). Identify new high-pressure oil rails by
                    the part number cast into the rail (Table 1).
                </para>
                <para>Old high-pressure oil rails can use either oil rail plug assemblies or attenuator assemblies
                    (Figure 1).
                </para>
            </geninfo>
        </description>
        <svcproc>
            <table id="t01" tblwidth="col-wide" frame="topbot">
                <title>New High-pressure Oil Rails</title>
                <tgroup cols="2">
                    <colspec colname="col1" colwidth="1.53*"/>
                    <colspec colname="col2" align="center" colwidth="1.02*"/>
                    <tbody>
                        <row>
                            <entry>
                                <para>
                                    <emph type="bold">Description</emph>
                                </para>
                            </entry>
                            <entry align="center">
                                <para>
                                    <emph type="bold">Part Number</emph>
                                </para>
                            </entry>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                            <entry>
                                <para>High pressure oil rail</para>
                            </entry>
                            <entry align="center">
                                <para>1847778C1</para>
                            </entry>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                            <entry>
                                <para>High pressure oil rail (w/o brake)</para>
                            </entry>
                            <entry align="center">
                                <para>1848234C1</para>
                            </entry>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                            <entry>
                                <para>High pressure oil rail assembly (w/o brake)</para>
                            </entry>
                            <entry align="center">
                                <para>1847785C91 or 1848235C91</para>
                            </entry>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                            <entry>
                                <para>Brake specific high pressure oil rail assembly</para>
                            </entry>
                            <entry align="center">
                                <para>1847786C91</para>
                            </entry>
                        </row>
                    </tbody>
                </tgroup>
            </table>
            <specpara>
                <caution>
                    <para>Installing an attenuator assembly in a new high-pressure oil rail may result in a
                        high-pressure oil leak and a loss of oil pressure.
                    </para>
                </caution>
            </specpara>
            <figure id="H11063" figsize="col-wide">
                <graphic filename="../tsifigures/H11063.webp" type="webp" scalefit="1" scalefitwidth="264px" box="no"/>
                <caption>Figure 1. Oil rail plug and attenuator assemblies</caption>
                <calloutgroup>
                    <callout1 type="arabic">Oil rail plug assembly 1854685C91</callout1>
                    <callout1 type="arabic">Attenuator assembly 1846058C91 (for use with old high-pressure oil rail
                        only)
                    </callout1>
                </calloutgroup>
            </figure>
        </svcproc>
    </tsi>
</isis>
